{"tid":1493982,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曾經有一個po 叫人唔好開烈士全名, 呢幾日又有個po 叫人唔好開被斬女士全名","createTime":"2019-08-21T13:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:22:44.000Z","uid":15644,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6df0c78eea37081273460ad8fa8397fb4e2d4343","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:00:18.000Z","msg":"求求大家唔好開烈士全名<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1232930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1232930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[突發] 烈士家屬冇反對過開烈士名<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳被斬女仔屋企人有嘢講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面講野一模一樣<br />\n無任何實質證據話自己係家屬朋友乜乜乜<br />\n叫人唔好講佢個名<br />\n根本fact check 唔到係唔係真係屋企人講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真定假我唔知<br />\n但係背後用意都幾類似"},{"pid":"e9717798a0e9dadeef1c6ea8bd107c74f5b9ebac","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e34e2ca2a01f95bcf7df62fd8f8f884ea16dc50","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b6110d72061a6399b6e909f65dbfdf2be34bb36","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"被砍傷女仔個朋友接受立場訪問有講，不過係砍傷當晚，而家唔知"},{"pid":"0d80223f37fade1426c12bf623e527f05d6223e8","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b6110d72061a6399b6e909f65dbfdf2be34bb36","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"被砍傷女仔個朋友接受立場訪問有講，不過係砍傷當晚，而家唔知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"搵唔到相關新聞"},{"pid":"945c979e71aa5c607f04fbd5b30be612369c8f97","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"立場當晚直播，佢朋友鹽水哥"},{"pid":"bfd6b2045c03bdca5356d4babb530fdc118f1971","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:16:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大家好 我係烈士家屬嘅朋友<br />\n因為我無連登acc，所以借朋友嘅一用。</span><br />\n以下係我作為家屬朋友嘅立場，<span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家唔好再公開烈士全名。</span>雖然知道通晒天，但可以的話，請唔好再擴散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一來比死者家屬空間</span>度過呢個咁困難嘅時刻，過多嘅關注同壓力會造成二次心理傷害。<br />\n二來d狗而家都要搞程序，萬一畀有心人放流料抹黑烈士點算？<br />\n<br />\n如果大家係為烈士同家屬好，知嘅人就默默在心中紀念，唔好再廣傳全名畀人起佢底<br />\n<br />\n對大家嚟講，佢係烈士；對記者嚟講，佢係新聞；但對家屬嚟講，佢係家人<br />\n6537<br />\n128<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">借朋友acc，我係個女仔嘅好朋友。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢屋企人話唔想透露佢嘅資料 <br />\n(立場已經改返做黃姓女子)</span><br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好再瘋傳同討論佢個名同背景。<br />\n<br />\n同埋澄清返佢唔係日本人。<br />\n<br />\n佢現時無生命危險，但未清醒，等佢清醒返再決定要唔要公開討論。<span style=\"color: red;\">但現階段請尊重佢屋企人嘅意向，請大家俾返啲空間佢哋。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫幫手推。"},{"pid":"c5eb245148dc385e3fb5ca3a2dd2451a125eb15c","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945c979e71aa5c607f04fbd5b30be612369c8f97","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"立場當晚直播，佢朋友鹽水哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/376700092993218/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F376700092993218%2F&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ogwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=fe834509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/376700092993218/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢段直播有冇呢?<br />\n我睇左少少 太長 搵唔到<br />\n邊位係鹽水哥?"},{"pid":"bfe05b8a40817740bc3a0e38881df67aee8d9f57","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"又幾似喎"},{"pid":"2f0aa097d3dc7faed846f9498db382a3b8b47bed","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5eb245148dc385e3fb5ca3a2dd2451a125eb15c","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945c979e71aa5c607f04fbd5b30be612369c8f97","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"立場當晚直播，佢朋友鹽水哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/376700092993218/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F376700092993218%2F&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ogwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=fe834509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/376700092993218/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢段直播有冇呢?<br />\n我睇左少少 太長 搵唔到<br />\n邊位係鹽水哥?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"佢同立場哥哥一齊跑去現場架，佢講呢講野鄺神喺度"},{"pid":"3d2db714425ad29f0b1a4c0f450de3927273561f","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f0aa097d3dc7faed846f9498db382a3b8b47bed","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5eb245148dc385e3fb5ca3a2dd2451a125eb15c","tid":1493982,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945c979e71aa5c607f04fbd5b30be612369c8f97","tid":1493982,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"立場當晚直播，佢朋友鹽水哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/376700092993218/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F376700092993218%2F&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ogwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=fe834509\"